    "name": "Embolsadora API - Complete Collection",
    "description": "Master collection for Embolsadora 4.0 Cloud API\n\nConsolidated endpoints across all features:\n- Tenants management\n- Users CRUD\n- User Role Assignments\n- Edge Device Management\n\n**Base URL:** {{baseUrl}}/api/v1\n**Authentication:** Bearer JWT Token (header: Authorization)\n**Multi-tenant:** X-Tenant-ID header or :tenantId in path\n\n**Quick Start:**\n1. Set {{baseUrl}} = http://localhost:8080\n2. Set {{jwt_token}} from auth endpoint\n3. Set {{tenant_id}} and {{tenantId}} (tenant UUID)\n4. Execute requests folder by folder",
